Sentencas: A Sm0.075Nd0.075Ce0.85O2-delta-Er0.4Bi1.6O3 bilayer structured film, which showed an encouraging performance in LT-SOFCs, was successfully fabricated by a simple low cost technique combining one-step copressing with drop-coating.
Titulo: High performance ceria-bismuth bilayer electrolyte low temperature solid oxide fuel cells (LT-SOFCs) fabricated by combining co-pressing with drop-coating
